参见  https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/python/jupyter-support
 1)命令行：pip install Jupyter   #网不好就可太难下了，smile
    参见https://jupyter.org/install.html
 2)创建一个.py文件，包含
 #%%
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib as mpl
import numpy as np

x = np.linspace(0, 20, 100)
plt.plot(x, np.sin(x))
plt.show() 
点击运行——RUN Cell——跳出jupyter扩展未装——点击install   参见https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=donjayamanne.jupyter

3）错误：'Kernelspec' module not installed in the selected interpreter (D:\Python3.7\python.exe).
 Please re-install or update 'jupyter'.
 
**********************以上都没有用****************
1）重换一个帐号VScode安装在D盘，Python3安装在D盘
2）新建一个py文件，复制
 #%%
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib as mpl
import numpy as np

x = np.linspace(0, 20, 100)
plt.plot(x, np.sin(x))
plt.show() 
运行
3）底部跳除需安装的安装，直至全部完成
4）重启VSCode即可
